						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone on the tank bund.</hi></p>						

						<p>Only the imprecatory portion of a bigger record is preserved on this stone. It is stated to have been composed by <hi rend="bold">Konnayya.</hi> The copyist's name is lost. The engraver's name is given as <hi rend="bold">Nāgōja.</hi></p>						

						<p>The characters are of about <hi rend="bold">9th century A.D.</hi></p>						

